mahāvyādhiratisārapramehādiḥ | mṛtyuduḥkhaṃ maraṇameva ||

<commentary>yamadūto yamapuruṣaḥ | grasto gṛhītaḥ | kālo mṛtyuḥ | sa hi pāśa iva pāśaḥ | narakamavīcyādikaṃ | buddhairiti buddhapraṇītamahāpratisarādirakṣāvidhibhiḥ ||</commentary>

yadīti | narake 'pi yadi nārakaṃ duḥkhaṃ samanubhūya varṣalakṣaṃ karmakṣayān manuṣyakarmākṣipto manuṣyeṣūtpadyata iti bhāvaḥ | vajreṇeti meghanādanirgatavajraśūcyā |
